special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Give Superman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: DEFENDING THE HELPLESS
special_powers.description: Superman can use Invincible. Modify the defense value of adjacent friendly characters by +1. This power can't be countered.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Give Superman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - BATMAN
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: HIDING BEHIND YOU
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action if he occupies hindering terrain or no opposing character can draw a line of fire to him. If you do, place him into a square of hindering terrain within 6 squares and line of fire.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - BATMAN
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: WEIRD RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: The first time Robotman would be KO'd this game, instead roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Turn him to the click number equal to the result. If Robotman began the game on the yellow starting line, when using Weird Resurrection add 4 to your result (max. 12).

special_powers.name: IT BELONGS TO NOBODY, NOW
special_powers.description: When placing objects during game setup, you may place your opponent's objects.

special_powers.name: SANITY IS A FLEETING THING
special_powers.description: Give Mr. Nobody a power action and choose an opposing character within range and line of fire and choose two slots on its dial that have standard powers. Until your next turn or until the chosen character's dial is clicked, the chosen character can't use the powers displayed in those slots, but instead can use powers as if the colors in those slots are exchanged.

special_powers.name: CONSTRICTING VINES
special_powers.description: Poison Ivy can use Smoke Cloud as if she has a range of 6. Opposing characters occupying squares with these Smoke Cloud markers must break away if not already required to do so. If those characters fail a roll to break away, after actions resolve give them an action token. If you can't, deal them 1 penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: NO MAN CAN RESIST ME; NOT EVEN SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Poison Ivy can use Mind Control. When she uses Mind Control she is not dealt unavoidable damage from using it and places an Enthralled token on the cards of hit opposing characters if they do not already have one. When she uses Mind Control and targets a single opposing characters within 3 squares, modify her attack value by +2.

special_powers.name: YOU WON'T LET ANYTHING HAPPEN TO ME
special_powers.description: Poison Ivy can use Super Senses. When Poison Ivy is targeted by an attack, you may remove her Enthralled token from an opposing character within 6 squares that isn't attacking and this turn Poison Ivy may use a standard defense power that character can use.

special_powers.name: LET ME REMIND YOU WHAT WILL MAKE ME HAPPY
special_powers.description: Poison Ivy can use Shape Change. Opposing characters with her Enthralled tokens can't target Poison Ivy unless all opposing characters on the map have her Enthralled tokens at the beginning of that action.

special_powers.name: STAND BACK AND WATCH A REAL HERO, BEETLE!
special_powers.description: Booster Gold can use Probability Control. He may use it an additional time each turn if one of those uses targets himself or a friendly character named Blue Beetle.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: TENSILE STRENGTH
special_powers.description: When Iron is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, he can use Sidestep and increases the damage dealt by his object attacks by 1.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: JOINING OTHERS
special_powers.description: When Tin is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, he can use Sidestep and when using Perplex may modify the chosen value (except damage) by +2 instead.

special_powers.name: CREEPING
special_powers.description: Creeper can use Sidestep and Stealth.

special_powers.name: LUNATIC LAUGH
special_powers.description: Creeper can use Incapacitate, but only as a close combat action. When he does, the area of effect is all opposing characters within 2 squares.

special_powers.name: BLOOD MAGIC
special_powers.description: When an adjacent friendly character takes damage from an opponent's attack, put a number of Blood Magic tokens on that friendly character's card equal to the damage taken. Even if this power is lost, that friendly character may be given a free action to remove one Blood token and use Perplex targeting itself.

special_powers.name: WHEN A BLACK CAT CROSSES YOUR PATH...
special_powers.description: Once per turn, when Black Cat moves through a square occupied by an opposing character, give that character a Bad Luck token.

special_powers.name: ...BAD LUCK FOLLOWS.
special_powers.description: Black Cat can use Probability Control, but only to reroll the attack rolls of opposing characters anywhere on the map with a Bad Luck token. When Black Cat uses Probability Control, after actions resolve remove all Bad Luck tokens from that opposing character's card.

special_powers.name: ENTANGLING ROOTS
special_powers.description: Druid can use Smoke Cloud. Opposing characters occupying squares with these Smoke Cloud markers must break away and can't automatically break away.

special_powers.name: DARK LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Witch can use Enhancement. UNIQUE MODIFIER - When an adjacent friendly character with the Mystical keyword makes a ranged combat attack, modify their attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: BATTLE MAGIC
special_powers.description: Warlock can use Empower. UNIQUE MODIFIER - When an adjacent friendly character with the Mystical keyword makes a close combat attack, modify their attack value by +1.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Give Superman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: USING MY STRENGTH
special_powers.description: When making an object attack, increase Superman's damage dealt by 1. Give him a free action if he's not holding an object to destroy an adjacent wall or square of blocking terrain, then roll a d6. 3 - 4: He holds a standard light object. 5 - 6: He holds a standard heavy object.

special_powers.name: IVY'S INFLUENCE
special_powers.description: When building your force, you may choose a friendly character that is named Poison Ivy or possesses Mind Control on its starting click. Superman has the keywords of that character in addition to his own.

special_powers.name: YES, I'LL FIGHT FOR YOU
special_powers.description: Superman begins the game with a Control token on his card. At the beginning of your turn, roll a d6. On a result of 1-3, remove a Control token from this card. On a result of 4-6, put a Control token on this card. When Superman has no Control tokens, opposing characters can use Mind Control, but only to target him. Give Superman a free action and remove a Control token to modify his combat values by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - BATMAN
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: STUDY YOUR ENEMIES WELL
special_powers.description: When an opposing character within line of fire hits with an attack, place a Study token on this card.

special_powers.name: I'VE DISCOVERED WHAT I NEED TO KNOW
special_powers.description: Batman can use Outwit as if he has a range of 8. When he does, if he removes a Study token from this card, he can either counter an additional power on the targeted character or this use of Outwit lasts until your next turn, even if this power is lost.

special_powers.name: WEIRD RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: The first time Crazy Jane would be KO'd this game, instead roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Turn her to the click number equal to the result.

special_powers.name: RIDING THE UNDERGROUND
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may roll a d6 that can't be rerolled. If you do, turn her to that click number and, at the end of your turn, you may return her to the click she began the turn on.

special_powers.name: WEIRD RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: The first time Mento would be KO'd this game, instead roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Turn him to the click number equal to the result.

special_powers.name: MENTO-INTENSIFIER
special_powers.description: Mento can use Mind Control and Phasing/Teleport. When he uses Mind Control, choose one: He may increase his attack value by +2 -or- Give hit characters an action token after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: WEIRD RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: The first time Negative Man would be KO'd this game, instead roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Turn him to the click number equal to the result.

special_powers.name: NEGATIVE SPIRIT
special_powers.description: Give Negative Man a power action to place adjacent a Negative Spirit bystander if there is not already one on the map.

special_powers.name: HOLLOW MAN
special_powers.description: While a friendly Negative Spirit is not on the map, Negative Man deals penetrating damage. While a friendly Negative Spirit is on the map, Negative Man can't be given move actions.

special_powers.name: 60 SECONDS
special_powers.description: Negative Spirit deals penetrating damage. If Negative Spirit isn't within 6 squares of a friendly character named Negative Man, immediately KO it.

special_powers.name: NEGATIVELY-CHARGED ENERGY BEING
special_powers.description: Negative Spirit can use Phasing/Teleport. When he is given a move action, after actions resolve, he may make a close combat attack as a free action, targeting any one opposing character occupying a square he moved through.

special_powers.name: POLITICAL EXPEDIENCY TO SAVE NEW KRYPTON
special_powers.description: Friendly characters with the Kryptonian keyword are wild cards.

special_powers.name: SUPERGIRL'S MOTHER, SUPERMAN'S AUNT
special_powers.description: UNIQUE MODIFIER - When Alura is adjacent to a friendly character named Supergirl or Superman, modify their attack values by +1.

special_powers.name: SERVE THE STRONGEST LEADER
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, the highest-point friendly character on the map not named DeSaad becomes his Master. When his Master damages one or more opposing character and actions resolve, you may remove an action token from DeSaad.

special_powers.name: COWERING SERVATOR
special_powers.description: DeSaad can use Toughness. When he is targeted by an attack and his Master is within 7 squares, you may choose to replace his defense value with the printed defense value of his Master.

special_powers.name: INNOVATIVE SADIST
special_powers.description: DeSaad can use Outwit. When he does, after actions resolve, he can use Perplex targeting the same opposing character.

special_powers.name: EACH HIT CRACKS MY CONTAINMENT
special_powers.description: Major Force can use Poison. When he does, he deals damage to all other characters within a number of squares equal to his click number. If he's on click #4 or higher, it deals penetrating damage.

special_powers.name: DARK MATTER BLASTS
special_powers.description: Major Force can use Precision Strike and can use Steal Energy with close or ranged combat attacks.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: DUCTILE
special_powers.description: When Copper is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, she can use Sidestep and when using Shape Change, increases her d6 result by 1.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: HIGH DENSITY
special_powers.description: When Lead is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, he can use Sidestep and when using Impervious, increases his d6 result by 1.

special_powers.name: HEART OF THE BRIAR PATCH
special_powers.description: Blackbriar Thorn can use Poison. He may use it normally, or instead deal 1 penetrating damage to all opposing characters within 5 squares that are occupying hindering terrain.

special_powers.name: I'LL LET YOU KNOW WHEN I SEE ONE, BOOSTER!
special_powers.description: Blue Beetle can use Perplex. He may use it an additional time each turn if one of those uses targets himself or a friendly characters named Booster Gold.

special_powers.name: GONE! GONE! THE FORM OF MAN; RISE, THE DEMON ETRIGAN
special_powers.description: Give Jason Blood a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with Etrigan WF #045 on the same click number.

special_powers.name: SORCEROUS WARDS
special_powers.description: Jason Blood can use Super Senses. Adjacent friendly characters that share a keyword with him can use Super Senses, but only succeed on a roll of 6.

special_powers.name: UNRAVEL YOUR SIMPLE MAGICKS
special_powers.description: Jason Blood can use Outwit and Probability Control. Adjacent friendly characters can't be targeted by opposing characters' Probability Control.

special_powers.name: POOF!
special_powers.description: The Wizard can use Shape Change. When he uses Shape Change and succeeds, you may place him within 4 squares and in the square he previously occupied immediately place a Tiger bystander.

special_powers.name: ILLUSIONS HIDE YOUR TRUE SURROUNDINGS
special_powers.description: When The Wizard is occupying hindering terrain or adjacent to blocking terrain, The Wizard can't be targeted by non-adjacent opposing characters.

special_powers.name: SPELLCASTING PRODIGY
special_powers.description: Apprentice can use Perplex, but can only target other friendly characters.

special_powers.name: DEMONFEAR
special_powers.description: Demon can use Perplex, but can only target opposing characters.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - SUPERMAN
special_powers.description: Give Superman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: BURN
special_powers.description: Superman can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When he does, increase the damage dealt to the target by 1 if they have two action tokens.

special_powers.name: SHIFTING FOCUS - BATMAN
special_powers.description: Give Batman a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with another character with this trait on the same click number.

special_powers.name: TWO TYPES OF BATARANGS
special_powers.description: Batman can use Energy Explosion and Incapacitate.

special_powers.name: WEIRD RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: The first time Elasti-Girl would be KO'd this game, instead roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Turn her to the click number equal to the result. If Elasti-Girl began the game on the blue starting line, when using Weird Resurrection add 4 to your result (max. 12).

special_powers.name: PROTOPLASMIC PHYSIOLOGY
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, you may choose tiny symbol, giant symbol, or colossal symbol. If you do, Elasti-Girl has the chosen symbol until she chooses again. If she chooses tiny symbol, modify her combat values by -1. If she chooses colossal symbol, modify her combat values by +1.

special_powers.name: MALLEABLE FORM
special_powers.description: Elasti-Girl can use Combat Reflexes and Regeneration.

special_powers.name: UPGRADE YOUR STUFF
special_powers.description: UNIQUE MODIFIER - Modify the attack value of adjacent friendly characters by +1. If that character has the Armor or Robot keyword, also modify their defense value by +1.

special_powers.name: I'M BETTER WITH ROBOTS
special_powers.description: Toymaster can use Support. When he does, increase the d6 result by 1 if the target has the Robot or Armor keyword and decrease it by 1 otherwise.

special_powers.name: FLYING GRAYSON
special_powers.description: Nightwing can use Sidestep. When he has no action tokens, he may use Sidestep twice this turn and may be given a free action to make a close combat attack.

special_powers.name: EVERY PERSON I KNOW IS AN AMALGAM OF TWO FROM YOUR UNIVERSE?
special_powers.description: When building your force, you may pay 25 points and put a standard character on your sideline, called an Amalgam. At the beginning of the game, equip the Amalgam to a standard friendly character (other than Nightlantern) that is higher points than the Amalgam's highest point value and link it to that character's dial. For the rest of the game, the Amalgam provides the below effect when equipped: EFFECT: At the beginning of your turn or when when this character is clicked, you may choose a standard power on the equipped dial. This character can use that power until your next turn or clicked.

special_powers.name: WHY ARE ALL OF YOU LAUGHING SO HARD?
special_powers.description: UNIQUE MODIFIER - Adjacent opposing characters modify their attack values by -1. Opposing characters modify their attack values by -1 when attacking Condiment King.

special_powers.name: SLIPPERY KETCHUP AND MUSTARD SPRAYS
special_powers.description: Condiment King can use Force Blast and Plasticity.

special_powers.name: ALL COLORS ARE CONTAINED IN ME
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, choose the color of a standard power. UNIQUE MODIFIER - Opposing characters' dials displaying a power of the chosen color modify thier defense value by -1.

special_powers.name: COLOR-BASED HYPNOTICS
special_powers.description: Crazy Quilt can use Mind Control. When he does, if the target's dial is displaying a power of the color chosen for his trait, he takes no damage from this use of Mind Control and he and any hit targets modify their attack values by +2 for this action.

special_powers.name: METAMORPHIC
special_powers.description: Element Man can use Plasticity, Shape Change, and Giant Reach. When he has no action tokens, Element Man can use Phasing/Teleport.

special_powers.name: A PERIODIC ARSENAL
special_powers.description: Give Element Man a free action and choose a standard attack and/or defense power. Element Man can use the chosen powers until your next turn, even if this power is lost. If Element Man chose both attack and a defense power, deal him 1 unavoidable damage at the end of your turn.

special_powers.name: SUPREMELY UNCORRUPTABLE
special_powers.description: Opposing characters of an equal or lower point value can't target Mary Marvel with Outwit, Perplex, or Probability Control.

special_powers.name: SHAZAM!
special_powers.description: The first time this power is revealed due to damage from an opponent's attack, stop turning the dial. Mary Marvel can use Regeneration. When she does, don't decrease the result by 2. This power can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: CONDUCTOR
special_powers.description: When Gold is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, he can use Sidestep and when he uses Leadership, he increases his d6 result by 1 and may remove an action token from another adjacent friendly character of a lower point value when he succeeds.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: LIQUID
special_powers.description: When Mercury is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, he can use Sidestep and when using Super Senses increases his d6 result by 1.

special_powers.name: GET DOC TO SAFETY!
special_powers.description: Other friendly characters with the Metal Men keyword don't have their move actions count against your action total and they may use the Carry ability, but only to carry Doc Magnus.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: CREATOR OF THE METAL MEN
special_powers.description: When Doc Magnus is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, he can use Sidestep and when using Support, increase the healing by 1.

special_powers.name: GONE, GONE O ETRIGAN! RISE AGAIN THE FORM OF MAN!
special_powers.description: Give Etrigan a free action if he began your turn on the map. Replace him with Jason Blood WF #029 on the same click number.

special_powers.name: ADEPT AT RHYMES & WORDING GAMES
special_powers.description: Etrigan can use Plasticity and Sidestep. While he's adjacent to an opposing character, he can't be targeted by nonadjacent opposing characters.

special_powers.name: HAVE A TASTE OF BURNING FLAMES
special_powers.description: Etrigan can use Energy Explosion. When Etrigan makes an attack and hits, after actions resolve he can use Smoke Cloud as a free action but must place at least 1 hindering terrain marker adjacent to a hit character.

special_powers.name: TEEKL THE DRAGGA-CAT
special_powers.description: Teekl begins the game attached to Klarion the Witch-Boy. When Teekl is attached, Kalrion the Witch-Boy can use Super Senses. Give Klarion the Witch-Boy a free action and either place an attached Teekl adjacent or attach an adjacent friendly Teekl.

special_powers.name: TO BLUE RAFTERS
special_powers.description: Klarion the Witch-Boy can use Sidestep, Stealth, and Phasing/Teleport.

special_powers.name: DON'T FADE AWAY!
special_powers.description: Teekl can use Super Senses. When he uses it and rolls a 3-4, immediately attach him to Klarion.  This can't be countered.

special_powers.name: COLLECTING SOULS FOR REDEMPTION
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game and when an opposing character is KO'd, place a Soul token on this card. Give Ragman a free action and remove a Soul token to modify his combat values by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SKULKING FROM SHADOWS TO ROOFTOPS
special_powers.description: Ragman can use Leap/Climb and Stealth.

special_powers.name: BACKWARDS MAGIC
special_powers.description: When you place your characters at the start of the game, you may turn Zatara to click 7. If you do, this game turn his dial counter-clockwise when he is damaged and clockwise when he is healed. This trait can't be ignored.

special_powers.name: SACRIFICE MYSELF TO SAVE THE UNIVERSE... AND ZATANNA
special_powers.description: Zatara can use Pulse Wave. When he does, he doesn't target friendly characters he shares a keyword with and he may choose that his damage value becomes 4 and is locked. If he chose to do so, after actions resolve, KO Zatara.

special_powers.name: THE ORIGINAL MAGICIAN
special_powers.description: Zatara can use Perplex and Probability Control. When he uses Perplex, he may modify the chosen value (except damage) by +2 if he targets another friendly character he shares a keyword with.

special_powers.name: WORLD'S FINEST
special_powers.description: Superman's powers and abilities can't be countered. If Superman is adjacent to a friendly character named Batman, Superman can use the Batman Ally team ability.

special_powers.name: WORLD'S FINEST
special_powers.description: Batman's powers and abilities can't be countered. If Batman is given an action while adjacent to a friendly character named Superman, Batman can use the Superman Ally team ability this turn.

special_powers.name: THE DARK KNIGHT
special_powers.description: Batman can use Sidestep.

special_powers.name: WEIRD RESURRECTION
special_powers.description: The first time The Chief would be KO'd this game, instead roll 2d6 that can't be rerolled. Turn him to the click number equal to the result.

special_powers.name: ASSEMBLE THE OUTCASTS AND FREAKS
special_powers.description: Give The Chief a free action and choose a friendly character within 6 squares and line of fire. That character can use Sidestep this turn.

special_powers.name: SECRET MASTERMIND OF THEIR CREATION
special_powers.description: The Chief can use Mastermind. When he does adjacent friendly characters are considered a lower point value.

special_powers.name: PROTECT YOU FROM YOURSELVES
special_powers.description: The Chief can use Outwit and Perplex. When he uses either you may choose a friendly character within 6 squares that shares a keyword and he may count range and draw lines of fire from the chosen character's square. At the end of your turn, if The Chief did not use Outwit, choose a friendly character within 6 squares that shares a keyword and that character's powers and abilities can't be countered until your next turn.

special_powers.name: ...AND THE BRAIN
special_powers.description: Monsieur Mallah begins the game with Brain attached. While Brain is attached, Monsieur Mallah can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Super Senses. At the beginning of your turn, you may remove Brain and place it adjacent, or attach an adjacent friendly Brain.

special_powers.name: DIABOLICAL BRAIN & INSIDIOUS SIMIAN
special_powers.description: Monsieur Mallah can use Leadership and Perplex. When Monsieur Mallah has Brain attached and succeeds with Leadership, he may also remove an action token from himself.

special_powers.name: A MAGNIFICENT MIND OF MALEVOLENT PURPOSE
special_powers.description: When Brain would be KO'd, you may instead attach him to his Monsieur Mallah & deal Monsieur Mallah 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: REVEAL MY TRUE PARENTAGE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of the game, you may choose an opposing character to be The Joker's Daughter's "Parent". At the beginning of your turn, you may choose a standard attack or damage power the "Parent" can use. She can use the chosen power until your next turn.

special_powers.name: IT RUNS IN THE FAMILY
special_powers.description: The Joker's Daughter can use Sidestep and Stealth.

special_powers.name: MURDEROUS JACK-IN-THE-BOX ON MY BACK
special_powers.description: Give Harlequin a free action and place adjacent a Jack-in-the-Box bystander token printed on this card, then immediately give it an action as a free action. After actions resolve, remove that token from the game.

special_powers.name: POP! GOES THE WEASEL
special_powers.description: Harlequin can use Pulse Wave. When she does, once per game you may choose that her damage value becomes 3 and is locked and she can't place Jack-in-the-Box tokens for the remainder of this game.

special_powers.name: WHILE THE GAME IS ON, I CAN DO ANYTHING
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose an opposing character within range and line of fire and choose one: It can't use items equipped to it until your next turn -or- choose a standard power that opposing character can use and The Joker can use it until your next turn.

special_powers.name: IF YOU WANT SOMETHING DONE RIGHT, YOU HAVE TO MURDER THEM YOURSELF
special_powers.description: The Joker can use Phasing/Teleport. Once per turn, when another friendly character within range and line of fire misses all targets of an attack and actions resolve, you may place The Joker and that friendly character in each other's squares.

special_powers.name: I'LL KILL EVERY BATMAN THERE EVER WAS OR EVER WILL BE
special_powers.description: The Joker can use Outwit and does not need line of fire when doing so. When the Joker uses Outwit, he may also counter a power on each other opposing character with the same name as his target.

special_powers.name: RAPIDLY MORPHING FRAME
special_powers.description: Give Metallo a free action and choose one: choose a standard attack power, and he can use that power until your next turn -or- modify his combat values by +1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: YOU'VE EXPOSED MY KRYPTONITE HEART
special_powers.description: Metallo can use Poison. When he does, he removes an action token from himself for each opposing character that took damage from his Poison and he deals penetrating damage to characters with the Kryptonian keyword.

special_powers.name: DARKSEID'S ASSASSIN
special_powers.description: When Supergirl hits with an attack, after actions resolve, give each hit character an action token. If one or more hit characters were unable to be given an action token, remove an action token from Supergirl. If one or more hit characters can use the Batman Ally, Justice League, or Superman Ally team ability, heal her 1 click.

special_powers.name: SCATTER THE HUMAN RABBLE
special_powers.description: Supergirl can use Super Strength and Quake. When Supergirl has two action tokens, she can use Quake as a free action.

special_powers.name: METALLIC PROPERTY: PRECIOUS
special_powers.description: When Platinum is within 3 squares of another friendly character with the Metal Men keyword, she can use Sidestep and when using Outwit, she can choose an additional power to counter on the target.

special_powers.name: TIME TO GO SOLO!
special_powers.description: When this click is revealed due to taking damage, stop turning the dial. You may immediately replace Alloy with characters from your sideline that each have a different name, the Metal Men and Robot keywords and are 50 points or less. These characters come into the game on their last non-KO click and are placed within 3 squares of the square Alloy last occupied. Place up to a number of these characters depending on the starting line Alloy began the game on: Yellow = 3; Blue = 4; Red = 7. If you do not place any, deal Alloy 1 unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: RESPONSOMETER COMBINATIONS
special_powers.description: Alloy can use Perplex and Shape Change.

special_powers.name: WORLD'S VILEST TEAM
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor & Joker's power and abilities can't be countered and their combat values can't be decreased.

special_powers.name: IT'S USUALLY ONE OF US THAT'S BEHIND EVERYTHING
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor & Joker can use Mastermind. Lex Luthor and Joker and other friendly characters of 20 points or more can use the Underworld team ability.

special_powers.name: EVERY WHICH WAY BUT SANE
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor & Joker can use Sidestep twice during your turn.

special_powers.name: INSANITY AND BRILLIANCE COMBINED
special_powers.description: Lex Luthor & Joker can use Perplex and Outwit. This Outwit can be used in addition to a use of Outwit from the Superman Enemy team ability.

special_powers.name: WORLD'S FINEST TEAM
special_powers.description: World's Finest's power and abilities can't be countered and their combat values can't be decreased.

special_powers.name: GOOD DISTRACTION, BRUCE
special_powers.description: Once per turn, when World's Finest misses all targets with an attack and haven't used the Duo Attack ability this turn, after actions resolve they may make a close or ranged combat attack.

special_powers.name: BRUCE WILL WIN AT ANY COST
special_powers.description: World's Finest can use Colossal Stamina, but take 2 unavoidable damage instead of 1 when using it.

special_powers.name: BRUCE TELLS ME WHEN TO DODGE AND WHEN TO TAKE THE HIT
special_powers.description: World's Finest can use Combat Reflexes and Toughness.

special_powers.name: WE WILL MAKE THINGS RIGHT AGAIN
special_powers.description: (200 points) Superman's combat values can only be modified by powers or abilities from characters with "Kingdom Come team ability symbol". Superman's powers and abilities can only be countered by powers or abilities from characters with "Kingdom Come team ability symbol".

special_powers.name: ISOLATED FROM THIS VIOLENT WORLD
special_powers.description: (35 points) Superman begins the game placed at least 6 squares from any starting area and not adjacent to another character. While on click 11, he can't be moved or placed. When he is the only character on your force or an opposing character critical hits another friendly character, you may turn him to click 7 and he can't be healed for the remainder of the game.

special_powers.name: I WANT TO FARM IN PEACE
special_powers.description: Superman can use Incapacitate with two targets and an attack value of 12. Hit characters can't make ranged attacks during their turn.
